    "spell": {
        "name": "Spirit of the Beast",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You bring out the spirit of another animal that lives within your companion. Its body morphs slightly to take on an aspect of the animal you choose to have it emulate\u2014for example, it might grow a pair of horns if the spirit is a bull or a tail if the spirit is a monkey. When you Cast this Spell, select from one of the following aspects.\n* **Aspect of Insight** Your companion gains a +1 status bonus to Perception checks to Seek, Survival checks to Sense Direction or Track, and Will saves.\n* **Aspect of Might** Your companion gains a +1 status bonus to Athletics checks, Intimidation checks to Demoralize, and Fortitude saves.\n* **Aspect of Swiftness** Your companion gains a +1 status bonus to Acrobatics checks, Stealth checks to Hide or Sneak, and Reflex saves.",
        "subtype": "spell",
        "spell_type": "focus",
        "rank": 2,
